Adding Change Recovery Rate Sub-KPI 23

Change Recovery Rate



1. Click on an empty space on the canvas, and from the visualizations pane select Card.
2.Drag or select ‘ ChangeRecoveryRate ’ into the Fields section.
3. Fill in the figures provided below for the necessary fields.
General:

Width=71
Position,
Horizontal=1145
Vertical=330
Title=Off
Effects =>

Visual:
